channel.title: the bugs and issues ive had
channel.description:
headcrab latch is classic purple n black gmod style error and doesent work half the time :frowning:
the part with multiple grinders is astronomically hard to jump
the catwalk parts first catwalk seems to be an invisible angled wall flinging me off at 2000 miles an hour
and security guards dont shoot zombies unles they are farther than 4 feet away
everything else is awesome though especially soldier ai, it makes me believe they are trying to kill me :freeman:
